 I gave a letter to the postman  </i>

856
02:07:08,090 --> 02:07:09,910
<i> He put it in his sack  </i>

857
02:07:11,670 --> 02:07:14,670
<i> Bright and early
next morning  </i>

858
02:07:14,780 --> 02:07:17,300
<i> He brought my letter back  </i>

859
02:07:17,400 --> 02:07:19,220
<i> She wrote upon it  </i>

860
02:07:19,320 --> 02:07:21,140
<i> Return to sender  </i>

861
02:07:22,420 --> 02:07:24,370
<i> Address unknown  </i>

862
02:07:26,520 --> 02:07:28,340
<i> No such number   </i>

863
02:07:54,170 --> 02:07:55,990
Hello!

864
02:08:00,250 --> 02:08:02,070
Hello!

865
02:08:07,420 --> 02:08:09,390
[Whistles]

866
02:08:09,500 --> 02:08:11,540
FedEx!

867
02:08:47,580 --> 02:08:49,400
[Door Alarm Beeping]

868
02:09:16,380 --> 02:09:19,310
- You look lost.
- I do?

869
02:09:19,420 --> 02:09:21,560
Where are you headed?

870
02:09:25,150 --> 02:09:26,970
Well, I was just about
to figure that out.

871
02:09:28,600 --> 02:09:30,770
Well, that's 83 South.

872
02:09:30,910 --> 02:09:34,740
<i>And this road here will
hook you up with l-40 East.</i>

873
02:09:34,880 --> 02:09:37,010
If you turn right,

874
02:09:37,110 --> 02:09:40,630
that'll take you to
Amarillo, Flagstaff,

875
02:09:40,730 --> 02:09:42,520
California.

876
02:09:43,670 --> 02:09:45,500
And if you head back
that direction,

877
02:09:45,590 --> 02:09:48,460
<i>you'll find a whole lotta nothin'
all the way to Canada.</i>

878
02:09:50,460 --> 02:09:52,280
I got it.

879
02:09:52,380 --> 02:09:54,450
All right, then.

880
02:09:56,920 --> 02:09:58,750
Good luck, cowboy.

881
02:09:58,840 --> 02:10:00,570
<i>- [Starts Engine]
- Thank you.</i>

